The fingerprints on this laptop

789
00:58:21,456 --> 00:58:24,292
weren't found on this remote control
you brought

790
00:58:25,668 --> 00:58:27,420
but on this plastic cup.

791
00:58:29,255 --> 00:58:32,592
You look like someone who just got dumped.

792
00:58:33,176 --> 00:58:34,260
I'll be right back.

793
00:59:04,916 --> 00:59:06,000
Dong-man.

794
00:59:15,677 --> 00:59:16,594
Professor Yu.

795
00:59:27,981 --> 00:59:31,276
I can't stop working on this case.

796
00:59:31,943 --> 00:59:34,153
No. I won't.

797
00:59:35,697 --> 00:59:37,323
You said the culprit is here.

798
00:59:39,993 --> 00:59:41,411
How did you…

799
00:59:41,494 --> 00:59:42,787
I must…

800
00:59:43,830 --> 00:59:46,249
catch the culprit at all costs.

801
00:59:47,792 --> 00:59:49,377
So that I can

802
00:59:50,628 --> 00:59:52,130
protect the people I love.

803
00:59:56,968 --> 00:59:58,595
I've made up my mind,

804
00:59:59,554 --> 01:00:00,680
so you should decide.

805
01:00:02,056 --> 01:00:03,433
I must…

806
01:00:04,892 --> 01:00:07,103
see the end of this case.

807
01:00:09,063 --> 01:00:09,897
Dong-man.

808
01:01:03,785 --> 01:01:08,706
You're not getting Sun-ho
involved in your private matter, are you?

809
01:01:08,790 --> 01:01:10,083
You did it, didn't you?

810
01:01:10,166 --> 01:01:12,460
We don't know if you were injured
while carrying out a sting operation

811
01:01:12,543 --> 01:01:14,379
or if you're just putting on a show.

812
01:01:14,462 --> 01:01:16,297
Is that really what you think?

813
01:01:16,381 --> 01:01:17,590
Do you know what this is?

814
01:01:17,674 --> 01:01:21,552
I got a report. It says that the sample
questions going around the students

815
01:01:21,636 --> 01:01:24,138
seem to be the exam paper
for Investigation Studies.

816
01:01:24,222 --> 01:01:26,683
He can't deny it. They even found
an envelope of money in his office.

817
01:01:26,766 --> 01:01:28,393
The arrest warrant will be issued soon.

818
01:01:28,476 --> 01:01:29,602
You'll have to hurry.

819
01:01:29,686 --> 01:01:32,230
We'll be able to save Professor Yu, right?

820
01:01:32,313 --> 01:01:34,273
I'm going to save your supervisor.

